WEBVTT	#Elemental Media Engine(TM) 2.17.0.0

00:00:00.00 --> 00:00:00.57


00:00:00.57 --> 00:00:02.37
Tonight, a Florida judge is temporarily

00:00:02.37 --> 00:00:04.24
blocking the release of photos, video,

00:00:04.24 --> 00:00:06.24
and other records connected to the investigation

00:00:06.24 --> 00:00:08.16
into the death of Bob Saget.

00:00:08.16 --> 00:00:10.38
The actor and comedian's family sued

00:00:10.38 --> 00:00:12.66
a Florida Sheriff and a medical examiner's office

00:00:12.66 --> 00:00:13.89
to block the release.

00:00:13.89 --> 00:00:17.28
The judge agreed it would cause them emotional distress.

00:00:17.28 --> 00:00:19.05
The medical examiner said last week

00:00:19.05 --> 00:00:22.68
that Saget suffered severe skull fractures, likely from a fall

00:00:22.68 --> 00:00:25.29
or from hitting his head on the headboard of his bed

00:00:25.29 --> 00:00:27.65
and ruled his death accidental.